headline: Omnipod Maker Hit A Buy Point. Here's Where To Pick Up Shares.
summary: Omnipod maker Insulet reported a robust earnings report in early August.  The insulin pump stock has been on the move ever since.  Insulet is tapping into a new market of more than 38 million people who may be potential users of its medical device.
